{"id":1493,"date":"2018-10-01T12:00:00","date_gmt":"2018-10-01T12:00:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/?p=1493"},"modified":"2021-03-30T10:04:59","modified_gmt":"2021-03-30T10:04:59","slug":"tocotoco-dong-hanh-cung-hon-100-cap-doi-trong-su-kien-ngay-hoi-hien-mau-ngay-chung-doi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/blogs\/tocotoco-dong-hanh-cung-hon-100-cap-doi-trong-su-kien-ngay-hoi-hien-mau-ngay-chung-doi\/","title":{"rendered":"TocoToco \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng h\u01a1n 100 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u201cNg\u00e0y h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfn m\u00e1u Ng\u00e0y chung \u0111\u00f4i\u201d"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/image-27.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1494\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>T\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, TocoToco \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng 400 ly tr\u00e0 s\u1eefa cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u201cB\u1ea1n hi\u1ebfn m\u00e1u \u2013 TocoToco ti\u1ebfp s\u1eefa\u201d.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n hi\u1ebfn m\u00e1u \u201cNg\u00e0y chung \u0111\u00f4i\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Vi\u1ec7n Huy\u1ebft h\u1ecdc, H\u1ed9i thanh ni\u00ean t\u00ecnh nguy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 Ban ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ebfn m\u00e1u qu\u1eadn C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t lu\u00f4n v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng, TocoToco v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ee3i \u00edch doanh nghi\u1ec7p g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh ngay t\u1eeb khi s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/file.hstatic.net\/1000360860\/file\/30.1_46132a0f427d495890d097b040052ede_grande.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>TocoToco \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb 400 ly tr\u00e0 s\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cti\u1ebfp s\u1ee9c k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi\u201d cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i sau qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh hi\u1ebfn m\u00e1u. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean TocoToco \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ni\u1ec1m vui khi g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u00fd ngh\u0129a n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/file.hstatic.net\/1000360860\/file\/30.2_14d7a4aec42a499bae8d747217ae8365_grande.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>TocoToco \u2013 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u tr\u00e0 s\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ly tr\u00e0 s\u1eefa ngon v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a TocoToco c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ngh\u0129a c\u1eed cao \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1i, \u201cl\u00e1 l\u00e0nh \u0111\u00f9m l\u00e1 r\u00e1ch\u201d c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/file.hstatic.net\/1000360860\/file\/30.3_8f7df9d88a564d8586ad883b34ab3d68_grande.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2013, TocoToco t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 h\u01a1n 200 c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0, tr\u00e2n ch\u00e2u thu\u1ea7n Vi\u1ec7t, tr\u00e0 s\u1eefa TocoToco lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh. TocoToco lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u0103n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/file.hstatic.net\/1000360860\/file\/3.4_f5b35331d6b946bc8b4f01551204bfad_grande.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a TocoToco t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/file.hstatic.net\/1000360860\/file\/30.5_9891b4f6210f41368e0ac65b3acb5c00_grande.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/file.hstatic.net\/1000360860\/file\/30.6_ba836e1b056949c98622c78cdd556046_grande.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, TocoToco \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng 400 ly tr\u00e0 s\u1eefa cho c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u201cB\u1ea1n hi\u1ebfn m\u00e1u \u2013 TocoToco ti\u1ebfp s\u1eefa\u201d. S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n hi\u1ebfn m\u00e1u \u201cNg\u00e0y [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":1494,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template